doc:
Converts a [`[T; N]`](prim@array) into an `Rc<[T]>`.

The conversion moves the array into a newly allocated `Rc`.

# Example

```
# use std::rc::Rc;
let original: [i32; 3] = [1, 2, 3];
let shared: Rc<[i32]> = Rc::from(original);
assert_eq!(&[1, 2, 3], &shared[..]);
```
